%N A332519 a(n) = 4*(n^2 + n - 2).
%C A332519 The first 6 nonzero values are the same as in A177723, but then they differ.
%H A332519 <a href="/index/Rec#order_03">Index entries for linear recurrences with constant coefficients</a>, signature (3,-3,1).
%F A332519 a(n) = A177723(n+5) for n = 1..7.
%F A332519 a(n) = 8*A000096(n-1).
%F A332519 From _Elmo R. Oliveira_, May 21 2026: (Start)
%F A332519 G.f.: 8*x^2*(2 - x)/(1 - x)^3.
%F A332519 E.g.f.: 4*(2 + (-2 + 2*x + x^2)*exp(x)).
%F A332519 a(n) = 3*a(n-1) - 3*a(n-2) + a(n-3).
%F A332519 a(n) = 4*A028552(n-1) = 2*A139570(n-1) = A028560(2*n-2). (End)
%t A332519 a[n]:=a[n]=4(n^2+n-2)
